metadata.name: Judgement
metadata.description:
Judgement is the first 1/1 piece of the Fears collection.
It features a judging gaze, the fear of being ridiculed, mocked, or looked down upon. 

Artist: Hannah | hahchu.eth
Digital Mixed Media
Collection : Fears

About the Artist: 
Hannah is a digital and traditional artist from Southeast Asia, with a passion for creating works that represent the facets of human emotion.
